Rating: 4
Pizza is a weeknight staple at our house (when made with dough from our local bakery) and this is GREAT one. The tangy, rich creme fraiche is wonderful with the potatoes. I did not peel the potatoes and parcooked them whole in the microwave with a touch of water to steam them. The potatoes turned out nicely browned and it was a great combination of flavors.

