Rating: 4
Delicious! I made 3 different pizzas and this one was the favorite. I made a few changes -- used rosemary instead of thyme and substituted a mixture of fresh goat cheese and milk (stirred to a smooth consistency) for the heavy cream. Will definitely be making this again.

Rating: 4
One note about this recipe: if you want to make smaller, individual pizzas on a cookie sheet (i.e. not fill up a whole pan as described), make sure to build up the crust of each pizza so that the cream does not flow onto the pan.

