What a nice variation from the typical pizza! The pizza not only tasted great but looked great, too. I used russets, as they were what I had on hand, and parboiled them for 7 to 8 minutes before slicing. I also used creme fraiche instead of the heavy cream. All in all, a tasty and unique pizza.

